[{"client_msg_id":"271ff092-1b09-4f63-8272-231358e994a4","type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"フォルダ丸ごとコピーで持ち運べるように。","ts":"1604470827.039100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"P8nG"}]},{"client_msg_id":"7c5e3bc4-50c3-48f8-a72e-b395d1ccaba2","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":":naruhodo:","ts":"1604470821.039000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Y/Vf9"}]},{"client_msg_id":"c3e33656-eb62-4c6f-bc16-4b5a999b1841","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"自分は `.vimrc` を置いて `$HOME/_vimrc` で読んでもらえるのを使う...","ts":"1604470816.038600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ZkU6q"}]},{"client_msg_id":"1b7f465b-1bae-4d79-bded-eb16652fdb91","type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"ですね","ts":"1604470796.037900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"MYp6"}]},{"client_msg_id":"4ac02d98-9d72-4525-b414-bb572b3ab424","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"\u0026gt; `$VIM/.vimrc`\nインストール先に入れてるのですか?","ts":"1604470776.037500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"zUB"}]},{"client_msg_id":"bbb28390-76e7-4054-9599-080f7a2aa468","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"あ、ちょっとちがった `~/.vim/info` だ","ts":"1604470740.036900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"oiyH/"}]},{"client_msg_id":"7bffe50a-93df-4e81-9353-0e73b3534942","type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"```set runtimepath^=~/.vim\nsilent! set packpath^=~/.vim\nset viminfo+=n~/.vim/viminfo```\nそんな手間でもないし、これでいいっかとなってる","ts":"1604470687.036500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"kBJ="}]},{"client_msg_id":"c02260c8-d84b-4dd0-8297-2c569f046479","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"まぁファイルパスは UNIX / Windows で共有してもほぼ意味がないので検索パターンくらいなんですけどね。","ts":"1604470477.035400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"jBq9"}]},{"client_msg_id":"7039024b-9378-4001-93c7-bfb13fe334ac","type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"`~/.vimrc` と `~/.vim/viminfo` にしてる。（Windowsだと `$VIM/.vimrc` と `$HOME/.vim/viminfo` なのでかなり変則的）","ts":"1604470390.034800","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"me-too","count":1,"users":["UAZ33BKV2"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"WBzR7"}]},{"client_msg_id":"57ea470a-abc3-48bf-9f82-5fc532fba47d","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"viminfofile、先頭に書かないと途中に書くと .viminfo が作られてしまうのでつらい。","ts":"1604470333.034300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"5j/"}]},{"client_msg_id":"5175e227-d545-45b2-b4f3-6795827153b2","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"せめて Windows でも `.vim` が行けるなら統一した vimrc が書けるのだけど。","ts":"1604470261.033100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"lNAF"}]},{"client_msg_id":"65801795-9E34-49B3-8FD3-22B6DAD975CA","type":"message","user":"U782D5DF1","text":"殺伐としたスレに `.exrc` が","ts":"1604470205.032500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"VIp=3"}]},{"client_msg_id":"51652a6c-a6a5-43b3-b6d4-65e93aaa5850","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"設定とデータわけて...まあ後付けならそうか...","ts":"1604470202.032400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ret"}]},{"client_msg_id":"1c55298c-4bc9-41ae-b708-a628039fee3e","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"`~/.vim/vimrc` が後付けなので、特に意味はないと思いますね…","ts":"1604470186.032100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Vcm"}]},{"client_msg_id":"847a1f33-c09a-48fb-8209-67116e706c67","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"いえ、関係はないですが、配置変えてるのはそういう方向性の意図があったのかなあ、という意味です。","ts":"1604470157.031300","edited":{"user":"UAZ33BKV2","ts":"1604470168.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"F5Y"}]},{"client_msg_id":"99983e90-4f13-47c0-aba5-cde03cb7baee","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"XDG は一切関係ないかと。 `~/.vim` が独自ディレクトリだし","ts":"1604470128.030500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"aHl"}]},{"client_msg_id":"f70a5b8a-b7f0-48bb-bcba-71c3e7181fe2","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"XDG_CONFIG_HOMEとXDG_DATA_HOMEみたいな棲み分けなんでしょうかねえ...","ts":"1604470093.030100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"xpm"}]},{"client_msg_id":"a6a999d0-e393-4dde-9a23-9a5ef0049ec6","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"vim script 書きたくないし。","ts":"1604469949.028900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"T6H9"}]},{"client_msg_id":"4a1cf5ab-1fdc-45e9-a394-5f51e8ab3ee4","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"最近 `~/.vim/vimrc` または `~/vimfiles/vimrc` にしてるので出来れば `~/vimfiles/viminfo` にしてほしい。","ts":"1604469930.028700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"uwkG"}]},{"client_msg_id":"1eb4111e-45e1-4aa0-b87a-6280e0457f11","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"viminfofile、vimrc と同じ場所をデフォルトにして欲しいな。","ts":"1604469902.027900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"2pS"}]}]
